Description: Provides a modular and reproducible ETL toolkit for the 
    Country-Level Institutional Assessment and Review (CLIAR) data. 
    It integrates external datasets (e.g., OECD, IMF, WDI, V-Dem) with metadata
    standards to support Shiny dashboards (cliarapp) and analytical workflows.
    The package standardizes data cleaning, metadata alignment, quality checks,
    global benchmarking (closeness-to-frontier CTF calculations) and coverage
    calculations across the CLIAR institutional clusters.
